{"id":278291,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/奇闻录-光腚男孩/","date":"2013-02-07T04:45:36Z","modified":"2013-02-07T08:16:00Z","title":"奇闻录 | 光腚男孩","content":"<p>2月3日至5日，李克强赴内蒙走访棚户区居民。当李克强在居民高俊平家坐下时，一位光屁股的小男孩抢镜。躲在被子里小孩先是爬入柜子，后又跳回床上钻进被窝。这一幕被摄像机逮个正着，并在6日的《新闻联播》中播出。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/%e5%a5%87%e9%97%bb%e5%bd%95-%e5%85%89%e8%85%9a%e7%94%b7%e5%ad%a9/8n43ddak00an0001/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-278313\"><img class=\" wp-image-278313 aligncenter\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8N43DDAK00AN0001.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8N43DDAK00AN0001.jpg 737w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8N43DDAK00AN0001-300x231.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 737px) 100vw, 737px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/%e5%a5%87%e9%97%bb%e5%bd%95-%e5%85%89%e8%85%9a%e7%94%b7%e5%ad%a9/8n43degd00an0001/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-278314\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-278314\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8N43DEGD00AN0001.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8N43DEGD00AN0001.jpg 737w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8N43DEGD00AN0001-300x230.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 737px) 100vw, 737px\" /></a></p>\n<p>网友猜测这一幕出现的来龙去脉：大人物突然来，家里娃儿还在光屁股睡觉，大人一想这样不礼貌，让娃儿躲进柜子里，本以为老李握个手就走，没想到李同学还坐下来，里面的娃呆久了受不了，你们聊你们的，我还是进被窝吧。</p>\n<p>1分04秒开始</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://news.cntv.cn/2013/02/06/VIDE1360150048961623.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\">点此</a>观看视频</p>\n<h3>猜你喜欢</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://qiwen.lu/10212.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">副市长智商捉急</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://qiwen.lu/9701.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">北京北京</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://qiwen.lu/9760.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">兰考弃儿</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://qiwen.lu/10590.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">反日爱国人士必看</a><